               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Sayfa Śǝllāse “The Sword of the Trinity” (fols. 5ra-76vb)
 I-1)
                     Introduction (fols. 5ra-10ra)
 I-2) Prayer for Monday (fols. 10ra-17ra),
                     followed by Miracle (fols. 17ra-18rb)
 I-3) Prayer for Tuesday (fols.
                     18rb-25va), followed by Miracle (fols. 25va-26va)
 I-4) Prayer for
                     Wednesday (fols. 26va-31va), followed by Miracle (fols. 31va-32rb)
 I-5)
                     Prayer for Thursday (fols. 32rb-38vb), followed by Miracle (fols.
                     38vb-40ra)
 I-6) Prayer for Friday (fols. 40ra-52ra), followed by Miracle
                     (fols. 52ra-53rb)
 I-7) Prayer for Saturday (fols. 53rb-59vb), followed by
                     Miracle (fols. 59vb-61ra)
 I-8) Prayer for Sunday (fols. 61rb-73ra),
                     followed by Miracle (fols. 73ra-75rb)
 I-9) Concluding prayer (fols.
                     75rb-76vb)
 
 Additiones 1-2.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="5ra" to="76vb"/>
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2296Sayfas">Sayfa Śǝllāse</title>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                        <locus from="5ra" to="10ra">5ra-10ra</locus>
                        <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2296Sayfas#Introduction">Sayfa Śǝllāse, Introduction</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡’’…
                           ንጽሕፍ፡ መቅድመ፡ ሰይፈ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ዘ፯ዕለታት፡ ተማኅፀንኩ፡ ብክሙ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ በከመ፡ አተውክሙ፡
                           ውስተ፡ ቤተ፡ አብርሃም፡…</incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                        <locus from="10ra" to="18rb"/>
                        <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2296Sayfas#Monday">Sayfa Śǝllāse, Praise for Monday</title>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.1">
                           <locus from="10ra" to="17ra">10ra-17ra</locus>
                           <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2296Sayfas#PrayerMonday">Prayer for Monday</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡’’… እነቅሕ፡ በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፨ እትነሣእ፡ በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡
                              አአትብ፡፡…</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.2">
                           <locus from="17ra" to="18rb">17ra-18rb</locus>
                           <title>Miracle 1: The
                              promises of the Persons of the Trinity to the faithful</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">ተአምራቲሆሙ፡... ወአሐተ፡
                              ዕለተ፡ ይቤ፡ አብ፡ ዘአክበረኒ፡ በምድር፡ አነ፡ አከብሮ፡ በመንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት።</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
                        <locus from="18rb" to="26va"/>
                        <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2296Sayfas#Tuesday">Sayfa Śǝllāse, Praise for Tuesday</title>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3.1">
                           <locus from="18rb" to="25va">18rb-25va</locus>
                           <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2296Sayfas#Tuesday">Prayer for Tuesday</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡’’… መለኮተ፡ ሥሉስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አኃትም፡ አኃትዎ፡ ከዋላየ: በመለኮተ፡ ሥሉስ፡
                              ቅዱስ፡…</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3.2">
                           <locus from="25va" to="26va">25va-26va</locus>
                           <title>Miracle 2: The demons
                              inside the beer</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">ተአምሪሆሙ፡... ወሀሎ፡ ፩ብእሲ፡ ወአሐተ፡ ዕለተ፡ ውስተ፡ ሀገረ፡ ፍልስጥኤም፡ ወረሰየ፡
                              ምዝረ፡ በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ለገቢረ፡ ተዝካሮሙ፡ ወመጽኡ፡ ብዙኃን፡ ሰይጣናት፡</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                     </msItem>   
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4">
                        <locus from="26va" to="32rb"/>
                        <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2296Sayfas#Wednesday">Sayfa Śǝllāse, Praise for Wednesday</title>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4.1">
                           <locus from="26va" to="31va">26va-31va</locus>
                           <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2296Sayfas#Wednesday">Prayer for Wednesday</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱ[ስ፡] ኅቡረ፡ ህላዌ፡ ሥሉስ፡ በተገጽዎ፡ አብ፡
                              ወወልድ፤ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ በጽማሬ፡ ሥሉስ፡</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4.2">
                           <locus from="31va" to="32rb">31va-32rb</locus>
                           <title>Miracle 3: The
                              governor angry with his troops who were doing the commemoration of the
                              Trinity</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">ተአምራቲሆሙ፡... ወሀሎ፡ ፩መኰንን፡ በሀገረ፡ ፍልስጥኤም፡ አዘዘ፡ ከመ፡ ይትጋብኡ፡ ሠራዊቱ፡ ሶበ፡
                              ርእየ፡ መኰንን፡ ከመ፡ ተጋብኡ፡ ሠራዊቱ፡ ይቤሎሙ፡ ዘገብረ፡ ተዝካሮሙ፡ ለአብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡
                              ቅዱስ፡</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                     </msItem>
                     
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5">
                        <locus from="32rb" to="40ra"/>
                        <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2296Sayfas#Thursday">Sayfa Śǝllāse, Praise for Thursday</title>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5.1">
                           <locus from="32rb" to="38vb">32rb-38vb</locus>
                           <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2296Sayfas#Thursday">Prayer for Thursday</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ በግፃዌ፡ ሥሉስ፡ በሥላሴ፤ ግፅው፡ ዋህድ፡
                              አምላክ፡ ፫አዕማደ፡ ብርሃን፡</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5.2">
                           <locus from="38vb" to="40ra">38vb-40ra</locus>
                           <title>Miracle 4: The promise
                              of the God Father to the faithful</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">ተአምራቲሆሙ፡... ወአሐተ፡ ዕለተ፡ ቦኡ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡
                              ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ውስተ፡ ጽርኃ፡ አርያም፡ ወሰረሩ፡ በውስተ፡ መናብርቲሆሙ፡ ለፌ፡ ወለፌ፡</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                     </msItem>
                     
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.6">
                        <locus from="40ra" to="53rb"/>
                        <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2296Sayfas#Friday">Sayfa Śǝllāse, Praise for Friday</title>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.6.1">
                           <locus from="40ra" to="52ra">40ra-52ra</locus>
                           <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2296Sayfas#Friday">Prayer for Friday</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡’’… አይ፡ ልሳን፡ ወአይ፡ ከናፍር፡ ዘይክል፡ ነቢበ፡ ዕበየ፨ ክብሮሙ፡ ለሥሉስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አይ፡
                              ልቡና፡</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.6.2">
                           <locus from="52ra" to="53rb">52ra-53rb</locus>
                           <title>Miracle 5: The words
                              of the Trinity toward the faithful</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">ተአምሪሆሙ፡... ወአሐተ፡ ዕለተ፡ ቦኡ፡ ውስተ፡
                              ሀገርፈ[sic]፡ ፈለገ፡ ጸቃውዕ፡ ወተናገሩ፡ ነገረ፡ ጥቀ፨ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ እንዘ፡ ይብሉ፡ ዝንቱ፡
                              ቃልነ፡</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                     </msItem>
                     
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.7">
                        <locus from="53rb" to="61ra"/>
                        <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2296Sayfas#Saturday">Sayfa Śǝllāse, Praise for Saturday</title>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.7.1">
                           <locus from="53rb" to="59vb">53rb-59vb</locus>
                           <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2296Sayfas#Saturday">Prayer for Saturday</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡’’… ሰላም፡ ለፍቅረ፡ መለኮት፡ በትስብእቱ፡ ዘጾመ፡ እንበይነ፡
                              ዚአነ</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.7.2">
                           <locus from="59vb" to="61ra">59vb-61ra</locus>
                           <title>Miracle 6: The God
                              Father announces the future Reign of the Trinity</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">ተአምራቲሆሙ፡... ወአሐተ፡ ዕለተ፡
                              አተዉ፡ ገጸ፡ አርያም፡ አብኒ፡ ጊዜ፡ ይመጽእ፡ ቃልየ፡ ሀለወኒ፡ ወይትሊዓል[sic]፡ በመዓዝናት። ይእዜሰ፡ ዘተለዓለ፡
                              ቃለ፡ ሰማዕት፡</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.8">
                        <locus from="61rb" to="75rb"/>
                        <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2296Sayfas#Sunday">Sayfa Śǝllāse, Praise for Sunday</title>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.8.1">
                           <locus from="61rb" to="73ra">61rb-73ra</locus>
                           <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2296Sayfas#Sunday">Prayer for Sunday</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡’’… አኃሥሥ፡ ዘእምኀቤከ፡ ጽድቀ፡ አቀመኒ፡ ጽድቅ፨ አኃሥሥ፡ ጥበበ፡ እምአከ፡</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.8.2">
                           <locus from="73ra" to="75rb">73ra-75rb</locus>
                           <title>Miracle 7: The Saviour
                              Jesus Christ resurrects the children fallen off</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">ተአምራቲሆሙ፡... ወአሐተ፡ ዕለተ፡ እንዘ፡
                              ይትለሐይ፡ ምስለ፡ ሕፃናት፡ በናዕሱ፡ ከመ፡ ደቂቅ፡ እስመ፡ ተመሰለ፡ ሰብአ፡ በኵሉ፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ኃጢአት፡
                              ባሕቲታ፡</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                     </msItem>
                     <note>The text of KTM-012 is arranged in the same way as <ref type="mss" target="ANLcr53">StrANL Conti Rossini 53 (StrANL 154-57)</ref> and <ref type="mss" target="BAVet177">Vat. Aeth. 177
                        (GréTisVat I, 637-42)</ref>, i.e. each daily prayer is
                        followed by a miracle; besides, the miracles and the prayers are the same,
                        with the exception of the miracle for Sunday (Miracle 7) and the concluding
                        prayer (Text I-9).</note>
                     <note>For the same miracles (except Sunday), s. also Ms. <ref type="mss" target="BAVet180">Vat. Aeth. 180
                        (GréTisVat I, 644-45).</ref></note>
                     <note>- Probably influence of Amharic or Tǝgrǝñña in some words: e.g., እጅ
                        (<locus target="#8va">8va</locus>) and ኸቢካኤል (<locus target="#72ra">72ra</locus>).</note>
                     <note>- Exchange of laryngeal; s., e.g., አአትብ, instead of አዐትብ (e.g., <locus target="#10va">10va</locus>, 10vb, 11rb).</note>
                  </msItem>
                  
